Anything in ()'s is optional, for "ambitious" people.

client
------
  send a message to server:
    a) login (real name)
    b) time
    c) IP (geographic coordinates lat/long)

server [RUN ON PORT 2300] [udp server]
------
  reads messages
  updates an sqlite3 database
    for each user/ip
      # of logins
      (geo coordinates)

admin
-----
  reads the database
